They are clearly making hiring decisions based on race. It was even mentioned during the interview that some of these people can't speak english. \n\nI believe the company might be helping to bring illegals here. I'm thinking about calling ICE. ", "author": "BillyBillington", "created": 1779508930311, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Seeker_17", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Race based hiring", "last_comment_created": 1779511825511, "content": "<p>Went on a job interview recently. This company produces electronic assemblies. They have about 40 people that work in the production area. The odd thing is, the city as a whole where this company is located has very few asian people. But the 40 people working in the production area are asian. Not every single one.. .but easily 95% of them are. Not just asian, but also female. There are two leads that are white men and the supervisor over this area is a white woman. I have to imagine the &quot;leads&quot; are only there to help translate documents and don't do any actual work. There's no way in hell in this city that 95% of your work force is asian. They are clearly making hiring decisions based on race. It was even mentioned during the interview that some of these people can't speak english.</p>\n<p>I believe the company might be helping to bring illegals here. I'm thinking about calling ICE.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 3, "score_up": 16, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": 